# Automated Bus Scheduling and Route Management System

A full-stack web application built for **Delhi Transport Corporation (DTC)** to automate bus scheduling, manage driver duties, and visualize routes on an interactive GIS map.

---

## Live Demo

- **Frontend:** https://bus-scheduling-system.vercel.app/
- **Backend:** https://bus-scheduling-system.onrender.com

### Demo Accounts

| Role | Email | Password | Access |
|------|-------|----------|--------|
| Admin | admin@dtc.com | admin123 | Full access |
| Scheduler | scheduler@dtc.com | scheduler123 | Manage schedules |
| Viewer | viewer@dtc.com | viewer123 | Read only |

