## API Endpoints

### Auth
| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|--------|----------|--------|-------------|
| POST | /api/auth/register | Public | Register new user |
| POST | /api/auth/login | Public | Login and get JWT token |
| GET | /api/auth/me | All roles | Get current user |

### Buses
| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|--------|----------|--------|-------------|
| GET | /api/buses | All roles | Get all buses |
| GET | /api/buses/:id | All roles | Get single bus |
| POST | /api/buses | Admin, Scheduler | Add bus |
| PUT | /api/buses/:id | Admin, Scheduler | Update bus |
| DELETE | /api/buses/:id | Admin only | Delete bus |

### Drivers
| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|--------|----------|--------|-------------|
| GET | /api/drivers | All roles | Get all drivers |
| GET | /api/drivers/:id | All roles | Get single driver |
| POST | /api/drivers | Admin, Scheduler | Add driver |
| PUT | /api/drivers/:id | Admin, Scheduler | Update driver |
| DELETE | /api/drivers/:id | Admin only | Delete driver |

### Routes
| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|--------|----------|--------|-------------|
| GET | /api/routes | All roles | Get all routes |
| GET | /api/routes/:id | All roles | Get single route |
| POST | /api/routes | Admin, Scheduler | Add route + overlap check |
| PUT | /api/routes/:id | Admin, Scheduler | Update route |
| DELETE | /api/routes/:id | Admin only | Delete route |

### Schedules
| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|--------|----------|--------|-------------|
| GET | /api/schedules | All roles | Get all schedules (populated) |
| GET | /api/schedules/:id | All roles | Get single schedule |
| POST | /api/schedules | Admin, Scheduler | Create schedule + conflict checks |
| PATCH | /api/schedules/:id/status | Admin, Scheduler | Update schedule status |
| DELETE | /api/schedules/:id | Admin only | Delete schedule |

---

## Setup and Installation

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+
- MongoDB (local or MongoDB Atlas)

### Backend Setup

```bash
cd backend
npm install
```

Create `.env` file in backend folder:
```
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
PORT=5000
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key_here
```

Start backend:
```bash
npm run dev
```

### Frontend Setup

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

Frontend runs on `https://bus-scheduling-system.onrender.com`
Backend runs on `http://localhost:5000`

### Seed Demo Data

Register demo accounts via Postman:

```
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
```

```json
{ "name": "DTC Admin", "email": "admin@dtc.com", "password": "admin123", "role": "admin" }
{ "name": "Ravi Scheduler", "email": "scheduler@dtc.com", "password": "scheduler123", "role": "scheduler" }
{ "name": "DTC Viewer", "email": "viewer@dtc.com", "password": "viewer123", "role": "viewer" }
```

